title: Episode 23: Lauren Lane
description:
On today's episode, Kailey sits down with her friend and fellow country wife, Lauren Lane! Kailey and Lauren talk about ALL the things! From Lauren's past relationships, to the story behind how her and her husband Chris Lane met, to motherhood, and to God speaking through dreams, they talk about it all.


Thank you to our partners!

Listen to The Snack Show with Jami Fallon here! https://anchor.fm/the-snack-show
